channel.title: Fast high uptime http proxy?
channel.description:
Hey, I'm looking for a fast http proxy that is almost always up. I had one a while ago but can't find it anymore. No, not one of those crappy cgi-web based proxies, just a IP and port number :)
Thanks.
PS. Please dont tell me to use google, trust me I have been looking for like 2 hours and every proxy is down, and those that are up are extremely slow.

item.title: Fast high uptime http proxy?
item.dc:creator: @Nerice Nerice
item.description:
@Nerice wrote:

If you just want it to hide yourself, planetlab has tons of them and one port on each is open to the public (lowest numbered port on the machine) . Several things about them though…

They do record what your doing, so if some site complains to them about you doing illigal stuff, they will give them your info.

http protocol only.

They have them all over the world, and they are very fast.
